in something else,

00:48:06.330 --> 00:48:08.197
but I just find it
personally interesting.

00:48:08.197 --> 00:48:09.530
So feel free to ask me anything.

00:48:09.530 --> 00:48:10.740
I love talking about it.

00:48:10.740 --> 00:48:11.960
Thanks so much guys.

00:48:11.960 --> 00:48:14.010
I really appreciate it.

